Hi there!

Come back after tracking your sleep tonight, or create your first entry below!
Place your phone next to you on the bed:

The smart alarm will wake you up within 30min (or your selected range) before your first alarm during lightest sleep.


(e.g. this is for an 8:30 AM smart alarm!)
